Package: upbm
Type: Package
Title: Tools for the analysis of universal Protein Binding Microarrays
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(person("Patrick", "Kimes", email = "patrick.kimes@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Dongyuan", "Song", email = "dsong@hsph.harvard.edu", role = "ctb"))
BugReports: https://github.com/pkimes/upbm/issues
URL: https://github.com/pkimes/upbm
Description: Classes and methods for the organization and analysis of transcription factor binding affinities
  quantified in vitro using universal protein binding microarrays (uPBMs).
